  keywords  = {THEORY (Philosophy), KNOWLEDGE, Theory of, CASE method, CASE studies, RESEARCH, DEFINITION (Logic), LOGIC, THOUGHT \& thinking, HYPOTHESIS, INDUSTRIAL research},
